I have a question, What I am?
Maybe this thing doesn't matter to our daily life you think.
But really?
I cann't tell which is right,but one important thing is that I love you.
I love you the warm spring sun;
I love you the fling happy bird;
and I love you the dreamed life;
I come back home looking at my daughter and son happily.
forget everything,my friend, forget evrything!
finally,you will only see one thing.
and that is you, my loved,just one day I seen the beautiful girl.
I just pass through the gray street.
the sun,you burned me with you...
